test_negate_of_divisors:
assert [] == [-6, -6, -6, -6, -6, -6, ...]
  Right contains 8 more items, first extra item: -6
  Full diff:
  - [-6, -6, -6, -6, -6, -6, -6, -6]
  + []
test_coefficient_of_divisor:
assert [6] == [12, 18, 24, 30, 36, 42, ...]
  At index 0 diff: 6 != 12
  Right contains 6 more items, first extra item: 18
  Full diff:
  - [12, 18, 24, 30, 36, 42, 48]
  + [6]
test_list_of_zeros:
assert [] == [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, ...]
  Right contains 8 more items, first extra item: 0
  Full diff:
  - [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0]
  + []
